VDR Plugin 'history' Revision History
-------------------------------------

2012-10-19: Version 0.0.3

- Support deleting history items through menu.
- Support deleting of also target files and recordings if enabled in setup.
- Support replaying of also non-VDR files using Xineliboutput Media Player.
- Bug fixes.

2012-10-10: Version 0.0.2

- Rename several classes to avoid class name clashes with other plugins.
  (Thanks to Rolf Ahrenberg for help with debugging)
- Bug fixes.

2012-10-07: Version 0.0.1

- Initial revision.
